{"tid":271883,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人次次食親薩莉亞都肚痾 仲要痾水柱？","createTime":"2017-06-05T12:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T14:45:36.000Z","uid":100227,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea93ae3db3c2470aa39d96b61d7fe5dd34935e2","tid":271883,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:08:48.000Z","msg":"第一次食 得我一個痾水柱 算 我當係咁啱我腸胃唔好<br />\n第二次食 兩個人去 兩個人都痾起碼三次 又係水柱黎 兩個人食啲嘢唔同 唯一一樣兩個都有做嘅就係用佢啲水杯飲水 <br />\n<br />\n結論係佢啲水杯真係超級污糟 以後都唔撚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693600759d4b7ff2f5f46fc449653812368e25ff","tid":271883,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"食同一間？"},{"pid":"81165e45d2e8c76da321dbc33aacb88527609714","tid":271883,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食同一間？</blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e0c21ca85cd9341e1d447f38e930bd2326384b","tid":271883,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"用熱水沖下先 是常識吧"},{"pid":"1548d5884e2ba8c462cd903c30b32ba726294ac4","tid":271883,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"見到杯水咁多油都知污穢啦<br />\n睇黎你係落左半斤砒霜都照飲果啲人黎"},{"pid":"114a674674707fdf318f35c22f389bc4c06753a7","tid":271883,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"唔飲水都會中伏啦<br />\n間野乜撚都好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853dee6d14e799e146bb464a5dff12abff9be20b","tid":271883,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食同一間？</blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就係嗰間問題囉"},{"pid":"f60dea40b44f47aca71e2f6d9a2f1a42900799c0","tid":271883,"uid":79763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2d08a42005d8a4f3089ab839ba236ec8063835","tid":271883,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"啲杯好油架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會飲佢啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c596cabff90faf0bc4420f8d3b3426cc5e55a8b9","tid":271883,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"當清下腸胃"},{"pid":"4b0a9d200a829c242f770690cff475a4ac11d7a2","tid":271883,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"下 一個月食五六次都冇事喎<br />\n利申 中染新開果間 用佢水杯飲可樂"},{"pid":"be6cf3f32f785e31515f5765e3831c8987f06078","tid":271883,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到杯水咁多油都知污穢啦<br />\n睇黎你係落左半斤砒霜都照飲果啲人黎</blockquote><br />\n我用熱水凍水交替沖左好多次先用都中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你再嘈話比你條女知有人送蘆薈比你"},{"pid":"e5eeef8ccd5e63b8a1378090079b18cb215d0dc3","tid":271883,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大角咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29248318b80cdb203ea611e998673eeaec4c4af7","tid":271883,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"個icon搞到成個post好撚戇柒鳩"},{"pid":"05fdf39b8f7532f2c9f123a86ae5