/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渣ga"},{"pid":"19f87c6192f4de036b489542b024ea4b90048bfd","tid":271883,"uid":63372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"薩莉亞係香港唔可以用佢D膠杯，唔可以飲佢D汽水，是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd5e55083bfdbf7569119d0a80550eec08f4b2a","tid":271883,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薩莉亞係香港唔可以用佢D膠杯，唔可以飲佢D汽水，是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔敢再食啦 上次痾左十幾分鐘痾到腳仔軟 下下都水柱咁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45880f69e6fd0b0fb5599b36048b19515d98398d","tid":271883,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個icon搞到成個post好撚戇柒鳩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實你想講除左腦魔icon 其實內容都講得幾啱</blockquote><br />\n食過唔同分店都未試過疴"}]}